---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Cannon Hill Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Cannon Hill Brisbane. Quiet inner-east suburb with strong community feel and consistent buyer demand. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Cannon Hill Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Cannon Hill Brisbane, serving the inner-east corridor.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/cannon-hill",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Cannon Hill", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/cannon-hill" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the median house price in Cannon Hill?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Cannon Hill's median house price is approximately $1.2 million as of early 2026. The suburb offers good value within Brisbane's inner-east corridor, with a mix of post-war brick homes, renovated Queenslanders and newer infill dwellings." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to sell a home in Cannon Hill?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Correctly priced Cannon Hill homes typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb's strong community feel and proximity to Cannon Hill Plaza and Morningside restaurant strip keep buyer demand steady throughout the year." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What makes Cannon Hill attractive to buyers?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Cannon Hill sits within easy reach of Morningside, Hawthorne and the Gateway Motorway, making it practical for families and professionals alike. The suburb has a quiet, established character and good local primary schools that resonate with family buyers upsizing from inner-city apartments." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Cannon Hill a good suburb to invest in?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Cannon Hill offers a relatively accessible entry point into Brisbane's eastern corridor with strong rental demand from professionals working across the inner east. Its price growth has been consistent as buyers seek value relative to pricier neighbours like Hawthorne and Bulimba." }
    }
  ]
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Cannon Hill</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Cannon Hill.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Cannon Hill and Brisbane's inner east.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/property-worth" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's Your Property Worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Quiet streets and consistent buyer demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Cannon Hill is a tightly held suburb with a strong sense of community and consistent buyer interest. Its accessibility, good schools and leafy character streets make it a firm favourite with families relocating to Brisbane's inner east.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      With an active buyer database and deep knowledge of this market, I understand exactly how to create competition for properties in Cannon Hill and the surrounding suburbs.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Cannon Hill Anglican College is a major drawcard for families, and properties within easy walking distance of the school consistently attract a larger field of qualified buyers. The Cannon Hill Shopping Centre on Wynnum Road provides everyday convenience that resonates strongly with families looking to simplify suburban life. Demand has been particularly strong for homes on the larger blocks that remain available in this suburb, with interstate buyers and upgraders competing for the same tightly held stock. Values have moved steadily upward as buyers recognise the relative affordability compared with neighbouring Morningside and Bulimba.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Cannon Hill Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner-east Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Tightly Held Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Consistent buyer demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/morningside" style="color:#c4912a;">Morningside</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carina" style="color:#c4912a;">Carina</a>, <a href="/suburbs/murarrie" style="color:#c4912a;">Murarrie</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION: FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Cannon Hill.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Cannon Hill?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Cannon Hill's median house price is approximately $1.2 million as of early 2026. The suburb offers good value within Brisbane's inner-east corridor, with a mix of post-war brick homes, renovated Queenslanders and newer infill dwellings.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Cannon Hill?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Correctly priced Cannon Hill homes typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb's strong community feel and proximity to Cannon Hill Plaza and Morningside restaurant strip keep buyer demand steady throughout the year.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What makes Cannon Hill attractive to buyers?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Cannon Hill sits within easy reach of Morningside, Hawthorne and the Gateway Motorway, making it practical for families and professionals alike. The suburb has a quiet, established character and good local primary schools that resonate with family buyers upsizing from inner-city apartments.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Cannon Hill a good suburb to invest in?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Cannon Hill offers a relatively accessible entry point into Brisbane's eastern corridor with strong rental demand from professionals working across the inner east. Its price growth has been consistent as buyers seek value relative to pricier neighbours like Hawthorne and Bulimba.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 3: SUBURBS SERVED
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#fff; padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Areas Covered</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Suburbs I specialise in.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:1.25rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
